TimeToLive TimeToLive

Edit

Gets or sets the messages time to live value. This is the duration after which the message expires, starting from when the message is sent to the Service Bus.Messages older than their TimeToLive value will expire and no longer be retained in the message store. Subscribers will be unable to receive expired messages.
